text: Sympleurotis rudis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1881. Costa Rica, Honduras, Guatemala, Mexico, and Panama.BioLib.cz - Sympleurotis rudis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1881
